gavl|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
gavl: gavl (Gmerlin Audio Video Library)
gavl:
gavl: Gavl is a low level library, upon which multimedia APIs can be built.
gavl: It handles all the details of audio and video formats like
gavl: colorspaces, samplerates, multichannel configurations etc. It provides
gavl: standardized definitions for those formats as well as container
gavl: structures for carrying Audio samples or Video frames. 
gavl:
gavl: http://gmerlin.sourceforge.net/
gavl:
